public class SensorNodeP2POutboundPort extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.ports.AbstractOutboundPort implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.network.interfaces.SensorNodeP2PCI

Description

The class SensorNodeP2POutboundPort acts as the outbound port that allows the connection between the sensor node component and the client component for the peer-to-peer communication service
